    %section#hero
      %h1 DEF CON Capture the Flag 2016
      %h2 Legitimate Business Syndicate
    %section#tagline
      %p
        We build innovative Capture the Flag games that pit hackers from around
        the world against the smartest analog adversaries and computerized
        challengers known.
      %p
        The future of Capture the Flag is now, and it's never been brighter.

    %section#dates
      #quals
        .quote
