      .justquote
        .quote
          .blockquote
            Defcon had some of the evilest, trickiest challenges I've ever faced
            in a CTF. And it was super fun because of it.
          .cite
            %a{href: 'http://capturetheswag.blogspot.com.au/2015/05/defcon-ctf-2015-cat-western-1-point.html'}
              CaptureTheSwag

      #finals
        .dates
          %h1 Finals
          %p
            The top hackers in the world battled it out head-to-head live
            at DEF CON in Las Vegas.
          %p.actual_dates
            August 5, 2016
            %br
            %em through
            %br
            August 7, 2016
        .quote
          .blockquote
            +1 to this - the organizers was fantastic this year. Infrastructure
            was amazingly solid, the room environment was comfortable, and the
            organizers were very open with communication.
          .cite
            %a{href: 'https://www.reddit.com/r/netsec/comments/1k1oh4/we_are_the_plaid_parliament_of_pwning_ask_us/cbkhxa6'}
              rzhou, PPP

    %section#prequals
      #howto
        %h1 Finals
        %p
          DEF CON CTF Finals were be held in the Bally's Event Center / DEF CON
          Contest Area, from August 5 to August 7.
        %p
          Thanks to our competitors, contestants, DEF CON staff, and everyone
          who visited our area for another successful year.
